Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/8xx: Allow pinning IMMR TLB when using early debug
 console
To: Benjamin Herrenschmidt <benh@kernel.crashing.org>,
        Paul Mackerras <paulus@samba.org>,
        Michael Ellerman <mpe@ellerman.id.au>
